OL,3,CThames Water drops bonuses due for
OL,4,Cbosses after Government criticism
OL,6,FThames Water has "withdrawn" plans to
OL,7,Fpay senior bosses large bonuses linked
OL,8,Fto the water company securing a #3
OL,9,Fbillion emergency loan, Environment
OL,10,FSecretary Steve Reed has said.
OL,12,FMr Reed confirmed the proposals had
OL,13,Fbeen dropped during an Environment,
OL,14,FFood and Rural Affairs (Efra)
OL,15,Fcommittee session with MPs on Tuesday.
OL,17,FEarlier in the day, Thames Water's
OL,18,Fchairman admitted to incorrectly
OL,19,Fstating that the so-called retention
OL,20,Fplan was "insisted upon" by the
OL,21,Fcompany's lenders.
