OL,3,CThames Water drops bonuses due for
OL,4,Cbosses after Government criticism
OL,6,FMr Reed told MPs that Thames Water had
OL,7,Fbeen "trying to circumvent" upcoming
OL,8,Frules that can ban water companies
OL,9,Ffrom paying bonuses, by "calling their
OL,10,Fbonuses something different so they
OL,11,Fcontinue to pay them".
OL,13,F"I'm very happy indeed that Thames
OL,14,Fhave now dropped those proposals," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"It was the wrong thing to do. It
OL,18,Foffends against their own customers'
OL,19,Fsense of fair play.
