OL,3,CThames Water drops bonuses due for
OL,4,Cbosses after Government criticism
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister's official
OL,7,Fspokesman said: "Water bosses
OL,8,Frewarding themselves for failure is
OL,9,Fclearly not acceptable and ministers
OL,10,Fare clear that, after presiding over
OL,11,Fyears of mismanagement, Thames Water
OL,12,Fshould not be handing itself bonuses.
OL,14,F"The new Ofwat powers that are set out
OL,15,Fin the Water Act and will be coming
OL,16,Finto effect shortly will be applied
OL,17,Fretrospectively, meaning that they
OL,18,Fapply to Thames Water, just as they
OL,19,Fwill any other company."
