OL,3,CThames Water drops bonuses due for
OL,4,Cbosses after Government criticism
OL,6,FThe regulator's new rules mean it can
OL,7,Fban bonus payments to water bosses if
OL,8,Fthey fail to meet standards to protect
OL,9,Fthe environment, their consumers, and
OL,10,Ftheir company's finances.
OL,12,FIt also means it could block payments
OL,13,Ffunded not just by customer money, but
OL,14,Falso by lenders and shareholders.
OL,16,FThames Water has said the retention
OL,17,Fincentives are different to
OL,18,Fperformance-related bonuses, so are
OL,19,Fnot covered by the rules, and will be
OL,20,Ffunded by lenders.
